		<description><![CDATA[<div><a href='http://rumandreason.com/2011/08/seeded-rye-and-wheat-loaf/'><img width="604" height="452" src="http://rumandreason.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/seededryewheatloaf-17-610x457.jpg" class="attachment-large wp-post-image" alt="Seeded rye and wheat loaf from Dan Lepard" title="Seeded rye and wheat loaf from Dan Lepard" /></a></div><br /><br />The bread that was made for Marmite. (Other nutritious spreads are available.) <br />
