			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><a href='http://rumandreason.com/2011/08/link-smorgasbord-for-august-2-2011/'><img width="604" height="452" src="http://rumandreason.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/Newfoundland-610x457.jpg" class="attachment-large wp-post-image" alt="Spiller&#039;s cove to French Beach trail" title="Spiller&#039;s cove to French Beach trail" /></a></div><br /><br /><p>Home from Newfoundland which was beautiful and <em>hot</em>&#8230; and now the possibility of proper weather back in the Bahamas with <a href="http://www.stormpulse.com/tropical-storm-emily-2011">Tropical Storm Emily</a> on the horizon. While I&#8217;m <a href="http://www.tripadvisor.com/members-reviews/rumandreason">Tripadvisoring</a>, reviewing and churning through the 967 photos I took (restrained, no?) I&#8217;ll update you with what I&#8217;ve been reading over the last couple of weeks. </p>
