<p class="zj_shareditems_source">from <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/food-and-drink" title="Life and style: Food &amp; drink | guardian.co.uk">Life and style: Food &amp; drink | guardian.co.uk</a></p>
